import React from 'react'; const ResendOTP = () => (

2-Step Verification

Enter the verification code generated by your phone ending in +xxx xxxxxxxx60.

+880
Security is critical in Bookstagram. to help keep your account safe, we'll text you a verification code when you sign in on a new device

Don't get code? Resend

) export default ResendOTP;
